Name: Fix Me Up Doc! – Dark Humor
About the game: A sausage on his left hand and ketchup on the right – a simulator of the most difficult profession in the world, that's surgery! But this isn't just a simple medical game with crazy operations. This is a parody game with dark humor , with such unbelievable graphics and so intense levels that you can even feel the smell. !!!No rugby players were harmed during the game development!!! Prepare your popcorn and play the funniest game you've ever played!
